WHERE TO SEND YOUR DONATION
===========================

Please read "help donation_sending" for information on how to send your
donation. Three people will collect all contributions:

    Lilith   (USA & Canada contributions)
    Marvin   (Swedish contributions only)
    Mercade  (Europe and international contributions, i.e. all others)

Your mud-name(s)
----------------

Along with your money, we want you to write your mud-name. We need your
mud-name so we can confirm the receipt and include your mud-name in the
list of contributors.

Conversion rates (August 15 1998)
---------------------------------

We suggested ten dollars. What does that mean in various other currencies?

Australia   AUS$ 16       Great Britain   GBP   6       Norway   NKR  75
Canada      CAN$ 15       Israel          NIS  40       Poland   PLZ  35
Denmark     DKR  68       Netherlands     NLG  20       Sweden   SEK  80
Germany     DM   18

If you live in a country that uses a different currency, please mail with
"Donation" to discuss which currency to send.

